import { Box } from '@mui/system'
import React from 'react'
import Banner from '../../Components/Banner/Banner'
import CardBanner from '../../Components/Banner/CardBanner'

import HomeBanner from '../../Components/Banner/HomeBanner'
import ProjectListing from '../../Components/Listing/ProjectListing'
import PropertyListing from '../../Components/Listing/PropertyListing'
import RecentlyAdd from '../../Components/SliderComponent/RecentlyAdd'

const Home = () => {
  return (
    
    <Box>
     
     <Banner />
     <CardBanner />
     <RecentlyAdd />
     <Box p={3} mt={2}>
      
     <ProjectListing />
       
       <HomeBanner />
          

       <PropertyListing />      
     </Box>
    
    </Box>
  )
}

export default Home
